S^{n-1} = \{x \in \mathbb{R}^n \mid \|x\|=1\}
f
 \frac{f(x)}{\|x\|} = f \left( \frac{x}{\|x\|} \right) 
f(e_1) \neq 0
e_1=(1,0,\ldots,0) \in \mathbb{R}^n
x=\varepsilon e_1
\varepsilon \in \mathbb{R}
\varepsilon \to 0
 \frac{f(\varepsilon e_1)}{\|\varepsilon e_1\|} = \frac{\varepsilon}{|\varepsilon|} \frac{f(e_1)}{\|e_1\|}, 
